753
00:45:01.784 --> 00:45:05.534
How are they contributing to the research program where they work?

754
00:45:06.084 --> 00:45:08.274
Is the specialist developing new approaches?

755
00:45:08.374 --> 00:45:12.164
Are they contributing new research directions?

756
00:45:12.224 --> 00:45:16.044
Some tips for building a strong application for the R50 is to

757
00:45:16.064 --> 00:45:19.984
focus on the specialist's past, present, and future contributions to

758
00:45:20.004 --> 00:45:23.954
the research program. So again, they're not proposing new research, so you should

759
00:45:24.064 --> 00:45:27.864
not be providing aims of what's going to happen over

760
00:45:27.904 --> 00:45:31.684
