765
00:45:46.204 --> 00:45:50.124
developing or adapting new technologies, training people within the lab

766
00:45:50.604 --> 00:45:53.833
or within the labs that they support, maintaining or initiating

767
00:45:53.924 --> 00:45:57.844
collaborations, and improving rigor and reproducibility in cancer research

768
00:45:58.224 --> 00:46:01.264
by establishing standardized protocols.

769
00:46:01.304 --> 00:46:04.844
And the unique background training and expertise of the specialist should be

770
00:46:04.864 --> 00:46:08.773
described, which supports the value of all of these activities that

771
00:46:08.804 --> 00:46:09.904
they perform.

772
00:46:11.264 --> 00:46:15.183
You should also describe the career goals and aspirations of the specialist.

773
00:46:15.204 --> 00:46:19.044
So again, this should be their research or their career path, so you should not be

774
00:46:19.084 --> 00:46:22.604
